lyrics:
[verse]
Brandon in his office, grinding all day
Writing rhymes, making beats, he's on his way
Stacking papers, chasing dreams, always on the move
No time for rest, he's got something to prove

[chorus]
In his office, he's the king of his game
Flowing like a river, his words are his flame
Brandon sitting, making magic, it's his groove
Hustling hard, there's nothing he can't smooth
